---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/PageLayout.astro";
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";
---

<PageLayout title="Valoración Inteligente" subtitle="Conozca el Valor Real">
  <section class="py-32 bg-background">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground font-light leading-relaxed">
          Nuestra valoración combina análisis de datos de mercado con el componente emocional único de cada propiedad. No somos algoritmos: somos expertos que entienden que cada casa tiene su propia historia.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <form class="bg-muted p-10 space-y-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-center mb-8">Solicite su Valoración Gratuita</h3>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <label class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-2 block">Nombre</label>
            <input 
              type="text"
              placeholder="Su nombre" 
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-border focus:border-accent focus:outline-none transition-colors"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-2 block">Teléfono</label>
            <input 
              type="tel"
              placeholder="600 000 000" 
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-border focus:border-accent focus:outline-none transition-colors"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <label class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-2 block">Email</label>
          <input 
            type="email"
            placeholder="su@email.com" 
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-border focus:border-accent focus:outline-none transition-colors"
          />
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <label class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-2 block">Dirección de la Propiedad</label>
          <input 
            type="text"
            placeholder="Calle, número, ciudad" 
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-border focus:border-accent focus:outline-none transition-colors"
          />
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <label class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-2 block">Metros²</label>
            <input 
              type="number"
              placeholder="120" 
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-border focus:border-accent focus:outline-none transition-colors"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-2 block">Dormitorios</label>
            <input 
              type="number"
              placeholder="3" 
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-border focus:border-accent focus:outline-none transition-colors"
            />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-2 block">Baños</label>
            <input 
              type="number"
              placeholder="2" 
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-border focus:border-accent focus:outline-none transition-colors"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <label class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-2 block">Cuéntenos sobre su propiedad</label>
          <textarea
            placeholder="¿Qué hace especial a su casa? Reformas recientes, características únicas, historia..."
            rows="4"
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 bg-white border border-border focus:border-accent focus:outline-none transition-colors resize-none"
          ></textarea>
        </div>
        
        <Button className="btn-premium w-full h-14" client:load>
          Solicitar Valoración Gratuita
        </Button>
        
        <p class="text-xs text-center text-muted-foreground">
          Le contactaremos en menos de 24 horas para coordinar una visita.
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
